    "1) Explain the Snowball concept.\n",
    "\n",
    "Ans:\n",
    "Snowball is a application that is used to transfer terabytes of data outside and inside of the AWS environment \n",
    "\n",
    "Data transferring using SnowBall is done in the following ways:\n",
    "i) A job is created.\n",
    "ii) The SnowBall application is connected.\n",
    "iii) The data is copied into the SnowBall application.\n",
    "iv) Data is then moved to the AWS S3.\n"
   ]
  },
